    <title>Next内置标签</title>
    <url>/2020/02/21/Next%E5%86%85%E7%BD%AE%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="Next主题内置标签"><a href="#Next主题内置标签" class="headerlink" title="Next主题内置标签"></a>Next主题内置标签</h2><p><strong>整理自<a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/tag-plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方文档</a></strong></p>
<p>Next主题提供了很多内置标签实现一些特殊的功能，官方<a href="https://theme-next.org/docs/tag-plugins/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">说明文档</a></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<p>标签插件是一种使Hexo支持的特殊样式内容的方法。例如，我们无法在标准Markdown中显示具有自定义尺寸的图像。然后我们可以使用标签插件来解决它。Hexo有很多标签可以帮助用户。Hexo还具有主题的接口，使主题能够创建自己的标签。NexT提供了以下标签：</p>
<ul>
<li>Centered Quote</li>
<li>Note</li>
<li>Tabs</li>
<li>PDF</li>
<li>Mermaid</li>
<li>Label</li>
<li>Video</li>
<li>Button</li>
<li>Caniuse</li>
<li>Group Pictures</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="一-Centered-Quote"><a href="#一-Centered-Quote" class="headerlink" title="一. Centered Quote"></a>一. Centered Quote</h2><blockquote>
<p>Centered Quote 标签可以使文本居中，对角各加一个引号，建议单行文本使用。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>用法：</p>
<figure class="highlight md"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% centerquote %&#125;Centered Quote&#123;% endcenterquote %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="xml"><span class="comment">&lt;!-- 标签别名 --&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% cq %&#125;Centered Quote&#123;% endcq %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果：</p>
<blockquote class="blockquote-center"><p>Centered Quote</p>
</blockquote>

<h2 id="二-note"><a href="#二-note" class="headerlink" title="二. note"></a>二. note</h2><blockquote>
<p>note标签可以突出显示一些信息。共有六种不同的类型，想要启用此功能需要打开主题配置文件Hexo\source\_data\next.yml,或者themes\next\_config.yml，找到note部分,style设置显示样式，icons设置是否显示图标。</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">note:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Note tag style values:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - simple    bs-callout old alert style. Default.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - modern    bs-callout new (v2-v3) alert style.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - flat      flat callout style with background, like on Mozilla or StackOverflow.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - disabled  disable all CSS styles import of note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  style:</span> <span class="string">simple</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  icons:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset lighter of background in % for modern and flat styles (modern: -12 | 12; flat: -18 | 6).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset also applied to label tag variables. This option can work with disabled note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">  light_bg_offset:</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>用法：</strong></p>
<h3 id="1-无样式时"><a href="#1-无样式时" class="headerlink" title="1. 无样式时"></a>1. 无样式时</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 标题</span><br><span class="line">不带有样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果</p>
<div class="note ">
            <h4 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h4><p>不带有样式</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="2-默认样式"><a href="#2-默认样式" class="headerlink" title="2. 默认样式"></a>2. 默认样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note default %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 默认样式</span><br><span class="line">默认样式效果。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果</p>
<div class="note default">
            <h4 id="默认样式"><a href="#默认样式" class="headerlink" title="默认样式"></a>默认样式</h4><p>默认样式效果。</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="3-主标题样式"><a href="#3-主标题样式" class="headerlink" title="3. 主标题样式"></a>3. 主标题样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note primary %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 主标题</span><br><span class="line">主标题样式效果。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>效果</p>
<div class="note primary">
            <h4 id="主标题"><a href="#主标题" class="headerlink" title="主标题"></a>主标题</h4><p>主标题样式效果。</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="4-信息样式"><a href="#4-信息样式" class="headerlink" title="4. 信息样式"></a>4. 信息样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">### 信息样式</span><br><span class="line">信息样式效果。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note info">
            <h4 id="信息样式"><a href="#信息样式" class="headerlink" title="信息样式"></a>信息样式</h4><p>信息样式效果。</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="5-成功样式"><a href="#5-成功样式" class="headerlink" title="5. 成功样式"></a>5. 成功样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 成功样式</span><br><span class="line">成功样式效果。</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note success">
            <h4 id="成功样式"><a href="#成功样式" class="headerlink" title="成功样式"></a>成功样式</h4><p>成功样式效果。</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="6-警告样式"><a href="#6-警告样式" class="headerlink" title="6. 警告样式"></a>6. 警告样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note warning %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 警告样式</span><br><span class="line">警告样式效果</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note warning">
            <h4 id="警告样式"><a href="#警告样式" class="headerlink" title="警告样式"></a>警告样式</h4><p>警告样式效果</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="7-危险样式"><a href="#7-危险样式" class="headerlink" title="7. 危险样式"></a>7. 危险样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note danger %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 危险样式</span><br><span class="line">危险样式效果</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note danger">
            <h4 id="危险样式"><a href="#危险样式" class="headerlink" title="危险样式"></a>危险样式</h4><p>危险样式效果</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="8-无图标样式"><a href="#8-无图标样式" class="headerlink" title="8. 无图标样式"></a>8. 无图标样式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info no-icon %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 无图标样式</span><br><span class="line">不带图标的效果</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note info no-icon">
            <h4 id="无图标样式"><a href="#无图标样式" class="headerlink" title="无图标样式"></a>无图标样式</h4><p>不带图标的效果</p>
          </div>

<h3 id="9-代码块标签演示"><a href="#9-代码块标签演示" class="headerlink" title="9. 代码块标签演示"></a>9. 代码块标签演示</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note success %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">#### 代码块样式</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% code %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endcode %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<div class="note success">
            <h4 id="代码块样式"><a href="#代码块样式" class="headerlink" title="代码块样式"></a>代码块样式</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br><span class="line">我是代码</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
          </div>

<h3 id="10-note表格标签"><a href="#10-note表格标签" class="headerlink" title="10. note表格标签"></a>10. note表格标签</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#### Table in Note</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% note default %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">| 1 | 2 |</span><br><span class="line">| - | - |</span><br><span class="line">| 3 | 4 |</span><br><span class="line">| 5 | 6 |</span><br><span class="line">| 7 | 8 |</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="Table-in-Note"><a href="#Table-in-Note" class="headerlink" title="Table in Note"></a>Table in Note</h4><div class="note default">
            <table><thead><tr><th>1</th><th>2</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>3</td><td>4</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>6</td></tr><tr><td>7</td><td>8</td></tr></tbody></table>
          </div>

<h2 id="三-tab选项卡"><a href="#三-tab选项卡" class="headerlink" title="三. tab选项卡"></a>三. tab选项卡</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs name %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">**This is Tab 1.**</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">**This is Tab 2.**</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">**This is Tab 3.**</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

